    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sliding rattles found in Indonesia. They are constructed from bamboo tubes with cut-back tongues, inserted into a frame; when the frame is shaken, the tubes slide back and forth.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
